<div id="review_90824113" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/90824113" />
    <a title="Winna" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/183839-winna"><img alt="Winna" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442479500p2/183839.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/90824113?book_show_action=true">Feb 21, 2010</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Winna" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Winna" href="/user/show/183839-winna">Winna</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/183839-winna?shelf=self-learning">self-learning</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/183839-winna?shelf=young-adult">young-adult</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/183839-winna?shelf=fantasy-myths-fairy-tales-magic">fantasy-myths-fairy-tales-magic</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer90824113" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10442782503270574282">My first DiCamillo read.<br/>I was blown away.<br/><br/>I thought this was a simple story about love. I was wrong about it being simple, because it showed how complicated life and love really were. It was touching, it was classic, it was.. very heartbreaking.<br/><br/>The first book to get me teary-eyed one of these days.<br/><br/>I love it.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


